OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry morning with sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Staying largely dry in the
OL,7,Fafternoon and turning cloudier. Rain
OL,8,Fmay edge into the far west of the
OL,9,FIsles later. Light winds becoming
OL,10,Fstrong southeasterlies in the west
OL,11,Flater with a risk of gales.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy with heavy rain
OL,14,Fspreading northeastwards. Becoming
OL,15,Flargely dry overnight with some
OL,16,Flighter rain lingering over the Isles.
OL,17,FStrong to gale force southeasterly
OL,18,Fwinds easing inland later in the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
