OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FOutbreaks of rain possible
OL,6,Fover the Isles but for many a dry day
OL,7,Fwith some bright or sunny spells.
OL,8,FBreezy inland with strong winds around
OL,9,Fthe coast, risk of gales.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy
OL,12,Foutbreaks of rain on Sunday. Sunny
OL,13,Fspells on Monday with scattered
OL,14,Fshowers. Dry with sunny spells
OL,15,FTuesday. Winds will be strong with
OL,16,Frisk of gales Sunday, then becoming
OL,17,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
